headline: Karat Packaging Stock Dips 5% Since Reporting Q4 Earnings Miss
summary: KRT reports a 21% year-over-year improvement in fourth-quarter 2024 earnings aided by 6% growth in revenues. The metric, however, fell short of expectations.
